WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:07.340
<i>The war between the Imperial Army and the 
Hellhorde has raged on for many years...</i>

3
00:00:09.110 --> 00:00:17.560
<i>In the midst of battle, the Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion</i>

4
00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:20.530
<i>falls into the hands of the Hellhorde.</i>

5
00:00:21.110 --> 00:00:26.390
<i>The Hellhorde, seeking to extract 
Imperial secrets from the princess...</i>

6
00:00:27.270 --> 00:00:30.500
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

7
00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:37.590
<i>...mercilessly subjects her 
to torture day after day.</i>

8
00:00:55.740 --> 00:00:57.380
At long last...

9
00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.730
Vengeance will be mine.

10
00:01:02.740 --> 00:01:03.790
Princess!

11
00:01:19.140 --> 00:01:26.480
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

12
00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:42.370
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

13
00:02:43.130 --> 00:02:46.370
What did you bring us 
all the way out here for?

14
00:02:46.370 --> 00:02:47.330
I know.

15
00:02:47.330 --> 00:02:49.850
I bet we're playing in the river, yeah.

16
00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:52.690
Let's just get this over with already.

17
00:02:52.690 --> 00:02:56.940
Well, I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

18
00:02:56.940 --> 00:02:59.850
It's not like I'd ever give in for 
splashing around in the river!

19
00:02:59.850 --> 00:03:02.020
Your Highness, you're way too excited.

20
00:03:02.420 --> 00:03:05.160
Today's torture shan't 
be playing in the river.

21
00:03:08.030 --> 00:03:09.640
Guh...

22
00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:11.240
Ah, I see.

23
00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:13.350
I wasn't looking forward to it at all.

24
00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:14.550
Poor thing...

25
00:03:13.350 --> 00:03:14.840
Do what you want.

26
00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:18.830
We've come to the river today for 
today's torture, marshmallows.

27
00:03:17.130 --> 00:03:18.840
Marshmallows

28
00:03:19.660 --> 00:03:21.110
Marshmallows?

29
00:03:21.110 --> 00:03:23.690
Sorry to say, but I'm not a huge fan.

30
00:03:23.690 --> 00:03:26.110
I don't like how they stick to your teeth.

31
00:03:26.510 --> 00:03:28.830
There's zero reason why I'd 
lose to today's torture!

32
00:03:28.830 --> 00:03:31.390
It's not too late to do something else!

33
00:03:32.530 --> 00:03:33.910
Like playing in the river!

34
00:03:33.910 --> 00:03:35.980
Do you want to play in the river that badly?

35
00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:39.850
I say marshmallows, but these 
are no ordinary marshmallows.

36
00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:44.300
They're roasted marshmallows!

37
00:03:44.860 --> 00:03:46.790
Roasted marshmallows?

38
00:03:46.790 --> 00:03:47.740
Indeed.

39
00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:51.580
We came all the way out here so 
as to safely start an open fire.

40
00:03:51.580 --> 00:03:52.520
Hmph!

41
00:03:52.520 --> 00:03:55.580
What good will roasting the marshmallows do?

42
00:03:55.580 --> 00:03:56.710
Yeah, that's right!

43
00:03:56.710 --> 00:03:58.280
You tell her, Your Highness!

44
00:04:10.820 --> 00:04:12.230
Ah! Wait, Your Highness!

45
00:04:12.230 --> 00:04:12.900
Stop!

46
00:04:13.350 --> 00:04:14.490
Princess.

47
00:04:14.490 --> 00:04:16.700
Would you care to try one, just this once?

48
00:04:17.520 --> 00:04:18.960
You mustn't, Your Highness!

49
00:04:18.960 --> 00:04:19.900
Don't fall for it!

50
00:04:20.140 --> 00:04:23.440
She's trying to teach you what 
roasted marshmallows taste like,

51
00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:25.690
so that you won't be able 
to resist their temptation!

52
00:04:26.180 --> 00:04:27.400
How devious!

53
00:04:27.710 --> 00:04:29.320
Why, I would never.

54
00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:32.470
'Twas simply a gesture of goodwill.

55
00:04:33.250 --> 00:04:34.790
Not to mention...

56
00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:38.580
She's the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

57
00:04:38.580 --> 00:04:44.480
That title is a testament to her 
strict self-discipline and training.

58
00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:50.090
Would she really succumb without resistance 
to the taste of roasted marshmallows?

59
00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:53.910
Your Highness won't fall 
for such an obvious ploy!

60
00:04:53.910 --> 00:04:54.920
That's right.

61
00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:56.930
Such an obvious ploy...

62
00:04:56.930 --> 00:05:01.260
I'd never succumb to some 
lousy roasted marshmallows!

63
00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:01.950
She fell for the obvious ploy!

64
00:05:03.850 --> 00:05:06.610
Even if it turns out to be good...

65
00:05:07.970 --> 00:05:10.990
I will never give in!

66
00:05:20.780 --> 00:05:22.910
<i>The soft texture of the marshmallow...</i>

67
00:05:23.130 --> 00:05:26.620
<i>Roasting has browned the 
surface and turned it crispy!</i>

68
00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:35.730
<i>And the heat has made the inside all gooey!</i>

69
00:05:35.730 --> 00:05:38.550
<i>The gooeyness is filling my mouth!</i>

70
00:05:49.990 --> 00:05:53.040
<i>A delight for the mouth!</i>

71
00:05:55.910 --> 00:05:57.550
Well, Princess?

72
00:05:57.550 --> 00:06:01.110
If you reveal a secret, I 
can let you have one more.

73
00:06:01.110 --> 00:06:02.790
Don't do it, Your Highness!

74
00:06:02.790 --> 00:06:04.050
Pull yourself together!

75
00:06:04.370 --> 00:06:05.860
It's okay, Ex.

76
00:06:05.860 --> 00:06:07.690
I'm as calm as can be.

77
00:06:07.690 --> 00:06:09.050
Your Highness!

78
00:06:09.050 --> 00:06:10.080
Hmph!

79
00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:12.660
One more if I tell you a secret?

80
00:06:12.660 --> 00:06:13.830
Keep it up, Your Highness!

81
00:06:13.830 --> 00:06:15.230
You've triumphed over the marshmallows!

82
00:06:15.670 --> 00:06:16.660
In other words...

83
00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:19.730
Will I get four marshmallows 
for four secrets?!

84
00:06:19.730 --> 00:06:21.050
She caved immediately!

85
00:06:21.420 --> 00:06:25.220
One secret, and you can 
have as many as you like.

86
00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:30.030
The princess
confessed

87
00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:31.540
So big!

88
00:06:30.110 --> 00:06:34.950
Jumbo

89
00:06:30.110 --> 00:06:34.950
Extra Large

90
00:06:31.540 --> 00:06:34.260
I didn't know they made 
marshmallows this big!

91
00:06:51.340 --> 00:06:53.230
Delicious!

92
00:06:53.230 --> 00:06:55.210
So gooey...

93
00:06:55.210 --> 00:06:58.920
Princess, while we're here, 
shall we play in the river?

94
00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.280
Wait, can I?!

95
00:07:00.280 --> 00:07:01.590
Of course.

96
00:07:02.180 --> 00:07:04.680
We're all done with you.

97
00:07:07.630 --> 00:07:08.990
Take that!

98
00:07:10.870 --> 00:07:11.660
How's that?!

99
00:07:11.660 --> 00:07:14.380
What do you think of today's secret?

100
00:07:14.380 --> 00:07:17.750
The castle guards are weak 
against fire attacks...

101
00:07:18.370 --> 00:07:22.420
But you know, it's normal for 
humans to be weak to fire.

102
00:07:22.420 --> 00:07:24.030
I suppose.

103
00:07:24.030 --> 00:07:26.880
Most creatures are weak against fire.

104
00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:30.050
What did you just say?!

105
00:07:30.050 --> 00:07:31.250
<i>Like I said...</i>

106
00:07:31.510 --> 00:07:35.760
If you're still by the river, get 
another secret out of the princess.

107
00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:40.530
His Majesty's orders.

108
00:07:41.270 --> 00:07:43.600
Call ended

109
00:07:41.270 --> 00:07:43.600
Call duration

110
00:07:47.300 --> 00:07:48.560
You've done it now!

111
00:07:51.330 --> 00:07:53.890
<i>Two torture sessions on the same day...</i>

112
00:07:53.890 --> 00:07:56.610
<i>I can only imagine the toll it will take!</i>

113
00:07:57.120 --> 00:08:00.470
<i>The princess's body might even give out.</i>

114
00:08:11.180 --> 00:08:13.710
What's with the long face?

115
00:08:13.710 --> 00:08:16.630
The Hell-Lord was unsatisfied 
with her work yet again.

116
00:08:16.630 --> 00:08:17.230
Huh?

117
00:08:17.540 --> 00:08:20.630
I kept an ear turned to her 
conversation on the phone.

118
00:08:20.630 --> 00:08:21.650
Ear?

119
00:08:21.650 --> 00:08:23.420
Where are your ears?

120
00:08:24.010 --> 00:08:27.060
It looks like she was ordered to carry 
out a second torture today.

121
00:08:27.330 --> 00:08:28.270
Wha—?!

122
00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:31.500
I-I can't handle two tortures in one day!

123
00:08:31.860 --> 00:08:35.050
Isn't that why she looks so troubled?

124
00:08:41.900 --> 00:08:44.010
Don't do it, Your Highness.

125
00:08:44.010 --> 00:08:46.670
Don't offer her a secret 
just because you feel bad.

126
00:08:47.250 --> 00:08:49.890
Y-You know I wouldn't do that!

127
00:08:49.890 --> 00:08:53.090
I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

128
00:08:53.740 --> 00:08:55.300
I've been in countless battles,

129
00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:58.130
cutting down my foes without any mercy.

130
00:08:58.680 --> 00:09:01.400
I would never take pity on my enemy!

131
00:09:01.710 --> 00:09:04.730
Worrying her pretty little head about me...

132
00:09:05.450 --> 00:09:07.770
She sure is a big ol' softie!

133
00:09:09.580 --> 00:09:10.740
She really is...

134
00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:13.560
as soft as they come.

135
00:09:16.060 --> 00:09:19.630
<i>I never imagined he'd instruct me 
to torture her twice in one day.</i>

136
00:09:19.630 --> 00:09:22.580
<i>The Hell-Lord truly is evil incarnate.</i>

137
00:09:23.430 --> 00:09:26.620
<i>No, a professional must perform her duty.</i>

138
00:09:26.620 --> 00:09:29.210
<i>His Majesty has the right idea here.</i>

139
00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:36.050
<i>Maybe... I'm not cut out to be a torturer.</i>

140
00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:54.200
Nice weather we're having today.

141
00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:56.260
Y-Yes, we are.

142
00:09:56.690 --> 00:10:00.060
The laundry dries faster on sunny days, too.

143
00:10:00.060 --> 00:10:01.940
Speaking of laundry...

144
00:10:02.630 --> 00:10:04.910
The king prefers wearing briefs.

145
00:10:05.790 --> 00:10:06.810
Princess!

146
00:10:06.810 --> 00:10:09.350
Why would you tell me such 
an important secret?!

147
00:10:09.350 --> 00:10:10.110
Huh?

148
00:10:10.110 --> 00:10:12.210
Did I let something slip just now?

149
00:10:12.650 --> 00:10:16.090
Are you taking pity on me, Princess?!

150
00:10:16.090 --> 00:10:18.920
I don't have a clue what 
you're talking about.

151
00:10:19.230 --> 00:10:21.220
But I like that look on your face.

152
00:10:22.500 --> 00:10:26.160
That depressed look really didn't suit you.

153
00:10:27.540 --> 00:10:28.980
Princess...

154
00:10:28.980 --> 00:10:31.840
Let's make the most of this perfect weather!

155
00:10:32.820 --> 00:10:33.980
Come play with me!

156
00:10:47.470 --> 00:10:48.950
I swear...

157
00:10:49.540 --> 00:10:51.160
Hey!

158
00:10:52.060 --> 00:10:53.970
Princess-chan!

159
00:10:54.630 --> 00:10:57.210
You-chan! In-chan!

160
00:10:57.540 --> 00:10:59.610
W-We're here.

161
00:10:59.610 --> 00:11:01.680
Done with torture for the day?

162
00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:02.410
Yep!

163
00:11:02.410 --> 00:11:05.100
I resisted for a while, but then I gave in.

164
00:11:05.100 --> 00:11:07.030
What are you doing here?

165
00:11:07.030 --> 00:11:11.520
W-We got a call from the grand inquisitor.

166
00:11:35.590 --> 00:11:38.090
Search

167
00:11:35.590 --> 00:11:38.090
#Torture #Riverbank

168
00:11:35.590 --> 00:11:38.090
Live Stream | Datarma Channel | Relaxing Torture by the Riverbank

169
00:11:35.590 --> 00:11:38.090
watching now

170
00:11:35.590 --> 00:11:38.090
Chat

171
00:11:53.430 --> 00:11:54.470
Princess!

172
00:12:46.670 --> 00:12:47.820
So cold!

173
00:13:13.310 --> 00:13:17.060
The princess
had fun

174
00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:19.930
What do you think?

175
00:13:20.250 --> 00:13:22.660
About the second secret for today.

176
00:13:23.330 --> 00:13:24.970
Huh? No good?

177
00:13:29.070 --> 00:13:31.990
The torture
will continue

178
00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:37.000
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

179
00:13:49.190 --> 00:13:52.550
Wow, check out that tan!

180
00:13:52.640 --> 00:13:56.060
Combat Soldier
Fourth Class
& Pain-Private
Giant

181
00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:56.020
It might sting if you 
soak in the hot springs,

182
00:13:56.020 --> 00:13:58.500
so let's go to the sauna instead today!

183
00:13:58.500 --> 00:13:59.640
The sauna?

184
00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:02.410
Wait, have you never been?

185
00:14:02.410 --> 00:14:03.150
Nope.

186
00:14:03.150 --> 00:14:04.450
What?

187
00:14:04.450 --> 00:14:07.220
You're missing out on something amazing!

188
00:14:07.220 --> 00:14:09.240
Okay, off we go!

189
00:14:11.430 --> 00:14:13.930
<i>I followed her after she said all that...</i>

190
00:14:14.040 --> 00:14:15.910
They're wearing towels with permission for the sake of the "torture"

191
00:14:15.900 --> 00:14:17.420
<i>But it's so hot!</i>

192
00:14:17.420 --> 00:14:20.360
<i>My entire body is dripping with sweat!</i>

193
00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:21.640
<i>This is supposed to feel good?</i>

194
00:14:21.640 --> 00:14:22.730
<i>Really?</i>

195
00:14:22.730 --> 00:14:24.670
<i>This is practically torture...</i>

196
00:14:25.580 --> 00:14:26.950
<i>So that's her deal!</i>

197
00:14:26.620 --> 00:14:28.760
It feels so nice!

198
00:14:26.950 --> 00:14:29.600
<i>Mama... no, Giant!</i>

199
00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:34.060
<i>Her sweet words lured me into this torture!</i>

200
00:14:34.800 --> 00:14:37.130
<i>If your average person were 
faced with this heat...</i>

201
00:14:37.130 --> 00:14:39.940
<i>I'm sure they wouldn't be able 
to bear it, and they'd end up talking.</i>

202
00:14:39.940 --> 00:14:44.270
<i>But I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.</i>

203
00:14:44.700 --> 00:14:48.090
<i>Be it a scorching desert 
or a frigid snowy mountain,</i>

204
00:14:48.090 --> 00:14:50.730
<i>I've fought while maintaining a clear head!</i>

205
00:14:50.730 --> 00:14:54.410
<i>I will never give in to this torture!</i>

206
00:14:54.490 --> 00:14:56.250
They're wearing towels with permission for the sake of the "torture"

207
00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:09.170
<i>Come to think of it, I haven't 
sweated this much in a long time.</i>

208
00:15:09.550 --> 00:15:12.990
<i>Lately, I eat three meals 
a day, get tortured,</i>

209
00:15:12.990 --> 00:15:15.610
<i>and spend the rest of my time 
lazing around and sleeping.</i>

210
00:15:15.610 --> 00:15:17.770
Munch, munch, munch...

211
00:15:17.770 --> 00:15:19.560
<i>I'd forgotten how this felt.</i>

212
00:15:19.870 --> 00:15:22.050
<i>It feels good to sweat it out.</i>

213
00:15:24.120 --> 00:15:25.890
<i>Feels good?!</i>

214
00:15:26.510 --> 00:15:27.940
<i>That can't be right!</i>

215
00:15:27.940 --> 00:15:30.820
<i>At first, this was nothing 
more than a blistering hell!</i>

216
00:15:30.820 --> 00:15:33.470
<i>Yet now, it feels good?!</i>

217
00:15:34.040 --> 00:15:36.250
<i>Being placed in this unusual situation</i>

218
00:15:36.250 --> 00:15:39.360
<i>is making my earthly suffering 
and troubles evaporate away!</i>

219
00:15:40.190 --> 00:15:43.320
<i>Ah, I see now, Giant...</i>

220
00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:44.960
<i>No, Mama!</i>

221
00:15:45.380 --> 00:15:49.040
<i>Saunas feel so nice!</i>

222
00:15:51.070 --> 00:15:53.730
Okay, I think it's about time we got out.

223
00:15:53.730 --> 00:15:55.480
Huh? Not yet...

224
00:15:55.930 --> 00:15:58.700
Staying in there too 
long's not good for you.

225
00:15:58.700 --> 00:16:00.730
Especially on your first time.

226
00:16:01.630 --> 00:16:03.220
Makes sense...

227
00:16:06.110 --> 00:16:09.060
<i>The air outside feels so nice and cool!</i>

228
00:16:09.460 --> 00:16:12.450
Okay, next up is the cold bath!

229
00:16:12.820 --> 00:16:14.030
Cold Bath

230
00:16:12.820 --> 00:16:14.070
C-Cold bath?!

231
00:16:14.450 --> 00:16:16.400
The water's at 17 degrees?!

232
00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:18.210
There's no way I can get in...

233
00:16:18.560 --> 00:16:22.320
<i>No, I thought the sauna was hot, too,</i>

234
00:16:22.320 --> 00:16:24.030
<i>but it ended up being really nice.</i>

235
00:16:25.990 --> 00:16:27.050
<i>All right!</i>

236
00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:34.460
<i>N-N-N-Nope, still cold!</i>

237
00:16:38.760 --> 00:16:39.730
<i>Huh?</i>

238
00:16:40.100 --> 00:16:42.060
Cold Bath

239
00:16:40.530 --> 00:16:42.070
<i>After getting used to it...</i>

240
00:16:42.070 --> 00:16:45.770
<i>the cold water feels nice on my warm body.</i>

241
00:16:45.770 --> 00:16:49.660
<i>The heat is slowly melting 
away from my body.</i>

242
00:16:49.660 --> 00:16:52.440
<i>I'm melting away, too!</i>

243
00:16:53.070 --> 00:16:56.110
<i>Ah, I'm becoming one with the water.</i>

244
00:16:56.450 --> 00:16:59.120
<i>It feels so good!</i>

245
00:16:59.490 --> 00:17:03.130
After a cold bath, take a nice, long break.

246
00:17:03.130 --> 00:17:06.410
<i>Ah, my arms and legs are tingling.</i>

247
00:17:06.410 --> 00:17:08.120
<i>I can feel the blood flowing through me.</i>

248
00:17:08.900 --> 00:17:11.810
<i>My body is being set free!</i>

249
00:17:12.400 --> 00:17:16.580
<i>Just now, I have become complete.</i>

250
00:17:20.310 --> 00:17:22.110
Thank you, Mama.

251
00:17:22.110 --> 00:17:24.800
I've learned the truth of the universe...

252
00:17:24.800 --> 00:17:28.050
no, of the sauna.

253
00:17:29.920 --> 00:17:33.160
They say lots of things about 
saunas and their detox effect,

254
00:17:33.430 --> 00:17:38.400
or how they may or may not 
help you lose weight.

255
00:17:38.850 --> 00:17:41.230
But none of that really matters.

256
00:17:41.650 --> 00:17:43.630
Saunas feel good!

257
00:17:43.630 --> 00:17:44.710
End of story!

258
00:17:44.710 --> 00:17:46.470
Yes, Mama!

259
00:17:46.470 --> 00:17:47.680
No...

260
00:17:47.680 --> 00:17:49.080
Master Mama!

261
00:17:51.170 --> 00:17:54.590
By the way, the
princess confessed

262
00:17:54.590 --> 00:17:56.450
Fair play, fair sauna!

263
00:17:54.590 --> 00:17:59.600
<i>Enjoy the sauna by following all rules and etiquette!!</i>

264
00:17:56.450 --> 00:17:59.580
Enjoy the sauna by following 
all rules and etiquette!

265
00:18:04.730 --> 00:18:07.930
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

266
00:18:08.200 --> 00:18:09.720
Where are we?

267
00:18:09.720 --> 00:18:10.730
And...

268
00:18:11.770 --> 00:18:13.160
who are <i>they</i>?

269
00:18:14.980 --> 00:18:16.580
Mad Kaiser!

270
00:18:16.580 --> 00:18:17.530
What?

271
00:18:17.920 --> 00:18:20.390
I've fought him in the past.

272
00:18:20.390 --> 00:18:22.550
Is that true, Your Highness?

273
00:18:22.550 --> 00:18:24.790
He was the boss of the Western Tower.

274
00:18:24.790 --> 00:18:26.040
I remember him well.

275
00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:28.180
This was him!

276
00:18:28.680 --> 00:18:30.140
You sliced him clean in half.

277
00:18:30.140 --> 00:18:31.460
No way that's him.

278
00:18:31.460 --> 00:18:34.110
Hey there! Is that you, Mad Kaiser?

279
00:18:34.110 --> 00:18:34.980
That's right!

280
00:18:34.980 --> 00:18:35.950
She was right!

281
00:18:36.550 --> 00:18:37.560
Princess.

282
00:18:37.560 --> 00:18:39.490
The wound you gave me...

283
00:18:39.490 --> 00:18:41.700
It throbs with pain to this day.

284
00:18:41.700 --> 00:18:43.300
That sure healed up nicely.

285
00:18:43.800 --> 00:18:44.830
I see.

286
00:18:44.830 --> 00:18:46.360
So that's what this is.

287
00:18:47.390 --> 00:18:51.490
Everyone here is someone 
I've defeated in the past!

288
00:18:51.490 --> 00:18:52.640
You can't be serious!

289
00:18:52.640 --> 00:18:54.380
That's not true at all.

290
00:18:54.380 --> 00:18:55.600
It wasn't true at all...

291
00:18:55.600 --> 00:18:58.210
Mad Kaiser just happened to be here.

292
00:18:58.210 --> 00:18:59.490
It's completely unrelated.

293
00:19:00.610 --> 00:19:04.970
Today's torture comes courtesy 
of Lieutorment Youki:

294
00:19:05.340 --> 00:19:06.740
a test of courage!

295
00:19:06.740 --> 00:19:08.290
Yay!

296
00:19:09.130 --> 00:19:13.450
These demons will act as the ghosts 
and hide in the school building.

297
00:19:14.090 --> 00:19:16.380
Lurking inside this abandoned 
school building,

298
00:19:16.380 --> 00:19:19.470
these scaring experts will provide 
you with a night of terror!

299
00:19:20.320 --> 00:19:22.580
Will you be able to withstand it, Princess?

300
00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:25.220
How underhanded...

301
00:19:26.420 --> 00:19:27.990
This is revenge for my wound!

302
00:19:27.990 --> 00:19:29.810
I'll scare you real good!

303
00:19:30.530 --> 00:19:32.180
You're scarier without the mask.

304
00:19:32.180 --> 00:19:33.610
All right, everyone!

305
00:19:33.610 --> 00:19:34.860
Let's get started!

306
00:19:34.860 --> 00:19:36.440
Yeah!

307
00:19:38.760 --> 00:19:39.940
Hold on.

308
00:19:40.410 --> 00:19:42.600
Courtesy of You-chan?

309
00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:44.100
Where's You-chan, then?

310
00:19:44.100 --> 00:19:46.070
Youki can't make it out today.

311
00:19:46.070 --> 00:19:46.810
What?!

312
00:19:47.280 --> 00:19:50.620
After sleeping with her stomach 
exposed, she's caught a cold.

313
00:19:50.620 --> 00:19:51.700
Oh, no!

314
00:19:52.100 --> 00:19:55.190
Which is why I'm administering 
this in her stead.

315
00:19:55.190 --> 00:19:56.910
You-chan's out with a cold?!

316
00:19:56.910 --> 00:19:59.350
Please, let me go and pay her a visit!

317
00:19:59.350 --> 00:20:00.290
I cannot.

318
00:20:01.570 --> 00:20:04.150
You're in the middle of being tortured.

319
00:20:04.150 --> 00:20:06.620
You shan't have freedom until it's over.

320
00:20:07.480 --> 00:20:09.560
But to put it in other words...

321
00:20:09.560 --> 00:20:11.530
You're free to go once it's over.

322
00:20:12.060 --> 00:20:13.020
Hmph.

323
00:20:13.020 --> 00:20:16.790
Do you think that helps the chances 
of Her Highness confessing?

324
00:20:16.790 --> 00:20:17.770
It's no use!

325
00:20:18.150 --> 00:20:21.600
Her Highness is the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

326
00:20:19.950 --> 00:20:24.290
There's a hidden passage leading to 
the castle in the Eastern Mountains!

327
00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:23.180
From a young age...

328
00:20:23.180 --> 00:20:24.090
That was quick!

329
00:20:24.090 --> 00:20:25.570
I didn't even get to the flashback!

330
00:20:25.890 --> 00:20:26.770
Very well!

331
00:20:26.770 --> 00:20:28.900
You've told us your secret, 
so we're done with you!

332
00:20:29.330 --> 00:20:30.900
Let's go and visit the sick!

333
00:20:35.250 --> 00:20:36.630
Seriously...

334
00:20:37.220 --> 00:20:39.730
You really made me worry.

335
00:20:40.170 --> 00:20:41.180
Sorry.

336
00:20:41.420 --> 00:20:44.510
But it was a pretty good torture idea.

337
00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:46.420
I gave in before I knew it.

338
00:20:46.960 --> 00:20:48.300
Here, drink up.

339
00:20:50.180 --> 00:20:51.600
Thanks.

340
00:20:51.600 --> 00:20:53.450
Do you have a fever?

341
00:20:53.450 --> 00:20:55.600
Does it hurt anywhere?

342
00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:57.340
Nah, I'm fine.

343
00:20:57.810 --> 00:21:00.530
It looks like her fever's gone down.

344
00:21:00.530 --> 00:21:02.580
I see, that's a relief.

345
00:21:05.400 --> 00:21:07.950
That feels so nice!

346
00:21:07.950 --> 00:21:10.400
Can you handle eating some congee?

347
00:21:13.860 --> 00:21:15.500
Here, You-chan.

348
00:21:19.230 --> 00:21:21.100
It's good!

349
00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:24.100
I might give in before I know it.

350
00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:29.210
Today's the one day where that's fine!

351
00:21:29.210 --> 00:21:30.820
Here, open up!

352
00:23:04.640 --> 00:23:07.690
How did you find today's secret?

353
00:23:08.100 --> 00:23:09.100
What?

354
00:23:09.100 --> 00:23:11.990
Is the hidden passage lit up?

355
00:23:11.990 --> 00:23:14.290
His Majesty would be scared in the dark?

356
00:23:14.290 --> 00:23:16.430
Yes, I'll ask.

357
00:23:16.740 --> 00:23:20.110
Also, the guys you took with you today.

358
00:23:20.110 --> 00:23:23.510
Administration is telling me they 
haven't clocked out for the day yet.

359
00:23:21.660 --> 00:23:26.660
